.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Movie-Genre: spy, family, fantasy, horror, comedy
Birthday: august, april, november, june, may
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Movie-Genre:spy == Color:red
2. Movie-Genre:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Movie-Genre:family == Birthday:june
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Birthday:april
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Pet:bird
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. Birthday:november is in the middle
9. Movie-Genre:horror is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == Birthday:august
13. Movie-Genre:fantasy == Cigar:prince
14. Movie-Genre:horror is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Birthday:may

.:: Answer ::.
